January 24, 1995	1.0 Initial effort                        (Jim Lynch)
May 12, 2003		1.1 Added NLS sort support            (Eric Auer, EA)
May 30, 2003		1.2 Improved i18n (KITTEN) usage                 (EA)
July 4, 2004		1.3 New languages. Enabled NLS sort by default,
                            replaced /N (enable) by /A (disable) switch  (EA)
July 9, 2004	        1.4 sort.exe/.com can sort max 395k/28k of data now
                            Old sort.com could only sort max 15k of data (EA)
September 23, 2007	1.5 added long file name support (Imre Leber)